    "long_instructions": "### DJ Sunshine needs sound effects for his 30-measure beat!\r\n\r\n**Do this:**\r\n- Pick 3 sound effects that match the music.\r\n- Set up 3 triggers to play each sound immediately when pressed.\r\n- Practice live coding with your triggers!",
